body_html:
http://ci.tensorflow.org/job/tf-master-win-gpu-cmake/
Looks like our continuous build is healthy. But our build uses VS 2015, and we do not set SIMD options.
So these may be the cause of the failure you are seeing.

The error message above is helpful, but still does not capture what compiler emits for that build target. Is it possible for you to file a new issue, and maybe share the full build output through pastebin?
